title: About Us
body:
OUR MISSION

It may sound unbelievable but the majority of the big companies in the cheese business usually do not invest much in the development of new technologies. Instead they rely on 3rd party solutions and cheeseware. Unlike theirs, our cheesing cheeseware was created, developed and designed in-house by us. Moreover, our business approach is human-oriented in that our cow support is a centre factor in the quality cheesing service that we offer.

title: Frequently Asked Questions
body:
Has Gandhi ever received the Nobel Prize?

No.

What is the airspeed velocity of an unladen swallow?

What do you mean, an African or a European Swallow?

How can I recover lost photos from my iPhone?

Very carefully. Hopefully you backed up your photos to iCloud or to your computer recently. Otherwise it will be expensive and difficult to recover if at all.

Why does my fish tank smell?

You need to clean your fish tank.

How do I stop my dog from going upstairs at night?

Get a kennel for him to stay in or use a baby gate to barricade the area you do not want him to go in.

What does the fox say?

  • Ring-ding-ding-ding-dingeringeding! Gering-ding-ding-ding-dingeringeding! Gering-ding-ding-ding-dingeringeding!
  • Wa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pow! Wa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pow! Wa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pa-pow!
  • Hatee-hatee-haee-ho! Hatee-hatee-haee-ho! Hatee-hatee-haee-ho!
  • Joff-tchoff-tchoffo-tchoffo-tchoff! Tchoff-tchoff-tchoffo-tchoffo-tchoff! Joff-tchoff-tchoffo-tchoffo-tchoff!

title: Contact Us
body:
